					    <h1>
                            Wal-Mart: An economic cancer on our cities                        </h1>

					    <h2>
                            In Asheville, N.C., a dense downtown generated jobs and tax revenue and restored the city's soul                        </h2>

					    <span class="byline"><a href='http://www.salon.com/writer/charles_montgomery/' rel='author' class="gaTrackLinkEvent" data-ga-track-json="[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;click&quot;, &quot;Charles Montgomery&quot;]" >Charles Montgomery</a></span>

